## ğŸ§ª Testing

Run the comprehensive test suite:

```bash
# Install test dependencies
pip install pytest pytest-asyncio pytest-mock

# Run all tests
pytest tests/ -v

# Run specific test file
pytest tests/test_framework.py -v

# Run with coverage
pytest tests/ --cov=src --cov-report=html
```

